Name: Duck Hunting
About the game: Welcome to the realistic world of duck hunting. Actions take place on a large, swampy terrain. The game has a system of earning points allows you to buy weapons and equipment for hunting. Experiment - a variety of guns, speed and camouflage, hunting alone or with a dog. Think and form your hunting tactics by tricking the ducks using decoy ducks. Shoot ducks , gaining experience!
